data.description: WELCOME HOME to this peaceful home located in the heart of Sarasota, within the HIGHLY DESIRABLE community of Tamaron! This spacious two bedroom home has been lovingly maintained by the same owner for over thirty years! Now it's time for someone else to begin to write their story within the walls of this home. This home sits on an oversized lot (a third of an acre!), on a corner lot in a quiet cul-de-sac, backing up to the nature preserve that is unique to Tamaron. You won't ever have to worry about having a neighbor beside or behind you! This thoughtfully-designed home has also been updated to include a large all-season room at the rear of the home, FULL of impact windows allowing for tons of natural light and allow you ample viewing opportunities of the preserve! This split-plan home includes walk-in closets in each bedroom and plenty of storage throughout. You will also find a storage shed built into the home on the side of the garage -- VERY convenient for those who enjoy working in their garage! You will also have peace of mind knowing the roof was replaced only two years ago (July 2021), HVAC updated in 2015 and hurricane protection is included! Be sure to schedule your showing of this home SOON!
